<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards are stipulated in accordance with Paragraph 1, Article 10 of the Charges and Fees Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Admission prices to the exhibition galleries of the National Museum of Prehistory (referred to as “the Museum” hereinafter) are as shown in Attached Table 1.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[As its operations permit, the Museum shall provide its venues for use by foreign and domestic public and private organizations or individuals for the holding of non-profit or social educational events that conform with the operational objectives of the Museum. Fee-charging standards for the use of venues are as shown in Attached Table 2.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Fee-charging standards for the use of the Museum’s pianos are as shown in Attached Table 3.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Fee-charging standards for the use of the Museum’s image materials and photocopy charges are as shown in Attached Table 4.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Admission prices to the exhibition room of the visitor’s center of the Museum’s Peinan Cultural Park are as shown in Attached Table 5.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Venue and facility management fees for the Museum’s Peinan Cultural Park are as shown in Attached Table 6.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 8</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Museum-issued “Family Card” discount ticket prices are as shown in Attached Table 7.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 8-1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Fee-charging standards prescribed here shall be reviewed at least once every three years to take into consideration various factors, such as prices of commodities and changes in market prices or costs.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 9</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards shall take effect immediately upon promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
